{"tid":1406273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷食] 紅底公司唔比員工8月5請假罷工!!!","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:42.000Z","uid":201244,"like":121,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f510e1b7d3d5263ac988bb6eb8f3e855c0d11eb6","tid":1406273,"uid":201244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"幫fd 開post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Gaia Group 紅底公司迫人撐送中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌！本身都知間餐廳係紅底<br />\n但為頭家都要返工<br />\n<br />\n但今次真係要出聲<br />\n之前老細係gp 到講要人去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聯署撐送中</span></span><br />\n個陣已經燥燥地！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/04/PsVrIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2FPsVrIM.jpg&h=232cb96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂大公司大老細<br />\n係到用職權去迫班細嘅去撐送中<br />\n完全係濫用職權！！<br />\n<br />\n今次8月5號大罷工<br />\n班細嘅想請假去罷工<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大老細高小姐話唔俾人8月5號放假！<br />\n(cap 唔到圖，驚自爆)<br />\n係全部人都唔會批假！！</span></span><br />\n之前迫人撐送中，宜家唔俾人請假罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一間公司可以表態撐送中<br />\n但唔代表可以要求所有職員都要係同一個立場</span></span><br />\n宜家Gaia Group係唔俾人有言論自由<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高小姐同譚詠麟好熟</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/04/rNlzcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2FrNlzcX.jpg&h=801e1426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近朱者赤，近墨者黑<br />\n高小姐都唔好得去邊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然佢咁想紅就俾佢紅！<br />\n宜家發動罷食Gaia Group 旗下所有餐廳！！<br />\n以下係旗下所有餐廳地址：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nIsola Bar &amp; Grill<br />\n中環港景街1號國際金融中心2樓2075號舖<br />\n<br />\n舍<br />\n中環港景街1號國際金融中心商場3樓3025-26, 3031-3066號舖<br />\n<br />\nGlasshouse<br />\n中環港景街1號國際金融中心4樓4009號舖<br />\n<br />\nGlasshouse<br />\n元朗元龍街9號形點一期1樓1028-1029號舖<br />\n<br />\nGlasshouse<br />\n太古太古城道18號太古城中心1樓101A號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreenhouse<br />\n銅鑼灣勿地臣街1號時代廣場食通天10樓1004號舖<br />\n<br />\n紅樓<br />\n中環蘭桂坊德己立街32號加州大廈23樓<br />\n<br />\n紅樓<br />\n銅鑼灣登龍街1-29號金朝陽中心2期Midtown1樓<br />\n<br />\n王家沙花樣年華<br />\n銅鑼灣登龍街1-29號金朝陽中心2期Midtown 1樓<br />\n<br />\n王家沙<br />\n旺角太子道西193號MOKO新世紀廣場2樓205舖<br />\n<br />\n王家沙<br />\n九龍塘達之路80號又一城G層23號舖<br />\n<br />\n王家沙花樣年華<br />\n紅磡黃埔天地享膳坊(第4期)地下G16號舖<br />\n<br />\n王家沙花樣年華<br />\n太古太古城道18號太古城中心2期1 樓101號舖<br />\n<br />\n颱風點心<br />\n銅鑼灣希慎道33號利園1期4樓401A號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n旺角太子道西193號MOKO新世紀廣場3樓301-302號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n沙田沙田正街18號新城市廣場一期1樓103A舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n中環港景街1號國際金融中心1樓1082舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n尖沙咀廣東道3-27號海港城海運大廈地下G01號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n九龍塘達之路80號又一城2樓L2-42號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n尖沙咀柯士甸道西1號圓方2樓2001號B舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n太古太古城道18號太古城中心二期地下007號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n將軍澳唐賢街9號PopCorn商場地下G05及G06號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n紅磡黃埔天地聚寶坊(第11期)地下1號及3號舖<br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute; Thai-pas Bar<br />\n銅鑼灣登龍街1-29號金朝陽中心2期Midtown 地下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">內幕爆料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.</span></span>Gaia Group 有係連登同open rice 請打手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">open rice 啲評分係假</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但當中都有不少負評<br />\n當中最經歷係呢個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/04/SdbCPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2FSdbCPG.jpg&h=6847e8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時在場<br />\n高小姐(Gaia gp 大老細)一直都對個煎堆好有興趣<br />\n剪緊個煎堆俾個客個陣走過黎話要試食<br />\n成班經理呆左<br />\n大佬呀！高小姐叫到，點敢唔俾呀<br />\n唯有剪多份俾佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大佬呀！堂堂大老細點解要好似乞衣咁食人地嘅嘢！</span></span><br />\n你叫廚房整份咪得<br />\n顯得原來高小姐係咁小家<br />\n連客人都可以敷衍<br />\n以為自己係老細就大曬<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個咁差嘅老闆管理嘅餐廳有點會好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過篇嘢講得啱<br />\nGaia Group 嘅餐廳好多都係得過且過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為咗慳成本，好多嘢都係淘寶</span></span><br />\n你話餐具飾物嗰啲係淘寶都算<br />\n連啲傢俬，枱，櫈都係淘寶<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都唔知有無經過檢驗<br />\n可能未必安全</span></span><br />\n遲啲坐爛左張櫈整親人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎大家打去食環報料</span></span><br />\n行內人都知，餐廳一定有曱甴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來海運間greyhound 特别多</span></span><br />\n<br />\nGreyhound Caf&eacute;<br />\n尖沙咀廣東道3-27號海港城海運大廈地下G01號舖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/04/5aXHFU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F5aXHFU.png&h=f00e77e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/04/ZpVxXg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2FZpVxXg.png&h=d75fbdc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能有好多巴絲都試係greyhound 見到曱甴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內幕係成個廚房都係曱甴<br />\n啲乾貨，蝦米成日有曱甴<br />\n放調味料個櫃全部都係曱甴屍體<br />\n成日都有客食到昆蟲要投訴</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對唔住，圖就無乜，因為好易自爆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然咁想出名就俾佢紅！！！<br />\n罷食Gaia Group 餐廳！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f59e10f7fb9b7d0178a2a2c71b5cfb815ef844fc","tid":1406273,"uid":147967,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"好撚嘔心 食蟲落肚 等我幫佢1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd82b0901c4c34fcdc680e198a34c33a9c1092d","tid":1406273,"uid":89121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e098ddbe2c7568f77e821752b44568cae9792bfb","tid":1406273,"uid":194588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe57b65435353c969d91ea5cf26f7c87019044dd","tid":1406273,"uid":109488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想嘔"},{"pid":"e5c9956d723f804099f3b8656b71b20e8c14fb67","tid":1406273,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f307fd2cb1415644d513da18adfe1e3d8770211","tid":1406273,"uid":161579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"罷食啦 支持送中條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafb3a900ab5802d1502cac33ed5fce55542b1bb","tid":1406273,"uid":237175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ecb513f67b511fb074269edfeec32a7a037c25","tid":1406273,"uid":237175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b1d2151aa794d7e67918233f843b133f417c3ec","tid":1406273,"uid":123738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"咁撚多蟲要報食環<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12f6f111c9c78e6bc71eca1ac37545159eec259","tid":1406273,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9741f27fa1b6a72375319816928d44bc574c06db","tid":1406273,"uid":219081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09f293e373fc43b129a81e61b1ad47f9f516374","tid":1406273,"uid":104357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾餐廳！<br />\n推爆佢！"},{"pid":"dae8b054d2eafa1cb8cb7d36e9c89982ced8908a","tid":1406273,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c6435f40fdc7b009d77688d0932d4b6227bb7ff","tid":1406273,"uid":82853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"屌 本身成日食glasshouse同greyhound<br />\n唔會再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012f2da41dd4d1ddf0c48b57db3fc320cd137c6a","tid":1406273,"uid":104357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f46644c735937053707eb4c5b62593362ec0e85","tid":1406273,"uid":161579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6435f40fdc7b009d77688d0932d4b6227bb7ff","tid":1406273,"uid":82853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"屌 本身成日食glasshouse同greyhound<br />\n唔會再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"茶餐廳都好食過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid