9-08-05T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"呢間野啲高層出名西 <br />\n老細成日拖糧 成日都推到好遲先簽名 <br />\n試過拖足半個月都未收到份人工<br />\n咁撚大間集團度縮到死<br />\n希望佢快啲執 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b0c56a63b3334dfb1a76e7f310b95b8a9e6239","tid":1406273,"uid":295355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"荷里活廣場有一知名化妝品牌經理（姓黃）<br />\n唔比我朋友請sick leave<br />\n該名經理稱自己腸胃炎都會番工<br />\n責罵我朋友沒有責任心，話：「可以比你抖 咁你幾點可以番番工？」<br />\n我朋友說：「我要睇完醫生之知喎」<br />\n經理說：「機會我一直都有比你，一係你老老實實同我講你今日唔番啦，咁之後啲更我抽起曬佢，你以後唔洗番。」<br />\n然後我朋友說「好。」<br />\n個經理窒左一窒：「姐係你之後都唔番啦下嘛？」<br />\n我朋友話：「係呀，我之後都番唔到啦」<br />\n最後仲被cut線。"},{"pid":"c71886c7c3350d673b746b76d4f2b6a2a09d785b","tid":1406273,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:26:11.000Z","msg":"三毛唔推 我幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8409e204978227cf3e92a97e4e258660d50cc314","tid":1406273,"uid":30674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"此post必火"},{"pid":"cfe78a735666e96a94e894a7249606e547bc2181","tid":1406273,"uid":230806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c1b107086554baa92f7e190ec1af506c323c329f","tid":1406273,"uid":54208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"點解上唔到熱門"},{"pid":"c79b2a867d0cab523507daaad475203578f31152","tid":1406273,"uid":42043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3088d0dea4c0048bd6c36dc7f8bf5a7667eb52d2","tid":1406273,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"罷食啦 支持送中條例"},{"pid":"ac8b329959be455c41c433716f4aa886597a2f4f","tid":1406273,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces